@startuml
actor "Khách hàng" as User
participant "RoomSearchService (JS)" as Frontend
participant "BookingController" as Controller
participant "BookingServiceImpl" as Service
participant "ICustomerRepository" as CustomerRepo
participant "IMembershipTierRepository" as TierRepo
participant "IRoomRepository" as RoomRepo
participant "IBookingRepository" as BookingRepo

User -> Frontend: 1. Chọn phòng + nhấn "Tạo booking"
Frontend -> Frontend: 2. Kiểm tra token
Frontend -> Controller: 3. POST /api/bookings (CreateBookingRequest)
Controller -> Service: 4. createBooking(username, request)
Service -> CustomerRepo: 5. findByUsername(username)
Service -> TierRepo: 6. getCustomerDiscountRate() → findTopByMinPoint...
Service -> RoomRepo: 7. findAllByRoomIds(roomIds)
Service -> RoomRepo: 8. findAvailableRooms(...) (kiểm tra trùng lịch)
Service -> Service: 9. Tính nights + tổng tiền SAU GIẢM GIÁ
Service -> Service: 10. Tạo Booking + List<BookingDetails>
Service -> BookingRepo: 11. save(booking)
Service --> Controller: 12. CreateBookingResponse (có discountRate, discountInfo)
Controller --> Frontend: 13. 200 OK
Frontend -> Frontend: 14. notify + redirectToVnpay(bookingID)
@enduml